<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>243</hymn_number>
<author>Sawikhawlien</author>
<title>Aw Bei Maiin</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gam lungsietum gam hi,
 A chungah ka lenga;
 Gitloh leh lungkhamna haw hin,
 Ni chengin ei bawm hi.

[V2]
 Aw, bei mai in (2)
 Khawvel gimum gam hi;
 Guolphahaw leh ka Hukdampa,
 Ngaia nichenga ka mauna.

[V3]
 2. Ka ngai kumsawt gam nuom,
 Lalpa Zion khawpi;
 Khawvel hi a nawpna pumin,
 A mang zel a nawpna.

[V4]
 3. Ka ngai ka Pa gam khu,
 Kikhen a um ta puoi;
 Mi thiengtho leh Angel vam haw,
 Ni chenga a lennau.

[V5]
 4. Gam lopi ka tun tieng,
 Ka vaihna lei gam hi;
 Ngaiin thil ta puong ka Lalpa,
 Na mel hawih ka muh tieng.</lyrics>
</song>